{"tid":1357762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十八鄉委員會＝中聯辦旗下，所以……","createTime":"2019-07-23T19:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T21:06:56.000Z","uid":255563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"74b2c32c9ee860e8b2e1e7bd846fc152273a61db","tid":1357762,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:26:55.000Z","msg":"遊行終點應該去嗰到？<br />\n<br />\n兩個好處，<br />\n1.唔洗入村（多真狗，除咗居民，普通人係唔會熟路）<br />\n2.聚焦官商鄉黑議題，同時，搞鳩到中聯辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啟發自：<br />\n【光復元朗要解決民鬥民，唔駛畀條命老黑嘅方法，就係圍18鄉委會】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1357545/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1357545/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d8effda79e47fb2006b14b39a03324bcbd25167b","tid":1357762,"uid":255563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:28:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hyknt.org/localDetail.php?id=7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyknt.org%2FlocalDetail.php%3Fid%3D7&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=3b068707\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hyknt.org/localDetail.php?id=7</a><br />\n<br />\n十八鄉 鄉事委員會<br />\n地址 : 元朗攸田東路一號"},{"pid":"b530e02c18082eb52879dec6c7314baa70657c0e","tid":1357762,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eebc452f1953e38aae3bcdb09f40014daf43cf0","tid":1357762,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:30:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a4122869ef3c48593669e9325929531446d7cf7a","tid":1357762,"uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:31:11.000Z","msg":"收到哂！"},{"pid":"236fb653e4e854962b202972e9fa6517862f1b38","tid":1357762,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:32:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a755f57b65b341ea99dccd96eb68c0bce17eccde","tid":1357762,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:32:48.000Z","msg":"支聯辦旗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aaf380ced2f01cb0f6661022d0626e78ece64c4","tid":1357762,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:34:47.000Z","msg":"點解要追擊何妖？ 因為他代表了西環想隻手遮天<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357773</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dae9f0414df72bf589e9ab9a3b0e4c982c57a609","tid":1357762,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:42:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d90aa9e82b9862fbd282048085d66619e95a48b8","tid":1357762,"uid":255563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:44:25.000Z","msg":"入面個post討論咗一啲野<br />\n<br />\n1.地理上，十八鄉委員會其實好近南邊圍<br />\n2.政治表態上，有一個涉及政權嘅象徵建築物做遊行終點，根據過往經驗。大家士氣好似會加100<br />\n<br />\n有一個象徵建築物做終點<br />\n好過入村做終點嘅其他原因包括：<br />\n1.入村畫面上難睇<br />\n2.實際操作難，真係要聲討／搞，搞邊戶？<br />\n3.多真狗（怕狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n4.少燈（怕黑）<br />\n最重要，係可以稍為將民眾鬥民眾嘅氣氛<br />\nSpin返去官商鄉黑，甚至係中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n如果當日口號係嗌中聯辦嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會怕比人講唔對準政權 ／失焦"},{"pid":"5facd9562e9db3e769418db909fa7ad16da96f95","tid":1357762,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:49:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"248beb1ad93feba7f20037d74253000a17769364","tid":1357762,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:50:43.000Z","msg":"認同代表性，但路線都好重要"},{"pid":"989f11207bd6010c0524487016fa0eef5dfbb35c","tid":1357762,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T20:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2288ced5709fbf557af1a5578faaba2aad8d381a","tid":1357762,"uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}